  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is designed to answer if an ergonomist can configure a daVinci robot console to
      improve surgeon discomfort. Adjustments to the robot console will be surgeon specific as they
      are tailored to their individual body type. Measurements will be taken at the time of console
      configuration.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
